I"
<p><a href="https://www.reddit.com/r/Deusex/comments/whs7ox/a_first_demo_in_my_project_to_recreate/">6th of August 2022, I made a post on reddit</a> about a little project that I‚Äôve been keeping quiet about for more than a year.</p>

<p>I took something that I threw together for the past month, added a camera and looked up how UE5‚Äôs sequence editor works, and made this.</p>

<iframe width="560" height="315" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/hReMq_UZFhc" title="YouTube video player" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture" allowfullscreen=""></iframe>

<p>This demo in particular combines the background in the VTOL‚Äôs interior as shown in the scene before you start the mission in the Manufacturing Plant and the helipad behind the SI building. The helipad set is very much a work in progress; I had to use some surfaces from the Megascans library for the helipad surface itself to make the demo look presentable.</p>

<p>The light used in the demo is directional, I rotated it a bit as the animation ran.</p>

