<p>fun fact: As far as I know, there are no scenes with Malik in the VTOL that are not pre-rendered. Now, they mention in the dev commentary that the scene where Jensen walks in the VTOL to talk to Sarif for the first mission was not supposed to be pre-rendered, but it turns out that the interior of the VTOL does come with textures, as well.</p>

<p>There‚Äôs a note there that says ‚ÄúInsha‚Äôallah day by day,‚Äù which I believe supports that bit in one of the novellas which mentions that Malik is Muslim. That‚Äôs pretty neat.</p>

